<div class="tool-panel notice-panel">
  <strong>SigmaStudio 4.7 引脚标注提醒 / Pin Label Notice</strong>
  <p>
    中文：从 SigmaStudio 4.7 开始，Pin 2 标为 “Limter ratio”，但实际是 limiter active flag；Pin 3 标为
    Limiter Active Flag，但实际是 limiter ratio。
  </p>
  <p>
    English: As of SigmaStudio 4.7, Pin 2 is labeled “Limter ratio” but is actually the limiter active flag, while Pin 3 is
    labeled Limiter Active Flag but is actually the limiter ratio.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel guide-panel">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>怎么选参数</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="guide-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>1. Threshold</strong>
      <p>限制器开始压缩的 RMS 阈值。超过该电平的信号会被压限。音频系统常从 -6 dB 到 0 dB 开始调试。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>2. 输入 RMS 估算</strong>
      <p>输入信号的大致 RMS 电平。仅用于估算增益衰减量，不影响实际参数计算，帮你判断限制深度是否合理。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>3. RMS Time Constant</strong>
      <p>值越大检测包络越快，能更快压住瞬态峰值；值越小越平滑，适合整体音量控制。调试起点建议 50 dB/s。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>4. Decay</strong>
      <p>值越大释放越快，越小恢复越慢。调试起点建议 12 dB/s。若听到明显的音量起伏（pumping），减小 Decay 值。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel preset-panel">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>场景预设</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="preset-row" aria-label="Limiter 参数预设">
    <button type="button" data-limiter-preset="safe">保护扬声器</button>
    <button type="button" data-limiter-preset="smooth">平滑限制</button>
    <button type="button" data-limiter-preset="fast">快速压峰</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="split-fields three">
  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="limiter-sample-rate-input">Sample Rate (Hz)</label>
    <input id="limiter-sample-rate-input" inputmode="decimal" value="48000" />
  </div>

  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="limiter-threshold-input">Threshold (dB)</label>
    <input id="limiter-threshold-input" inputmode="decimal" value="0" />
  </div>

  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="limiter-input-level-input">输入 RMS 估算 (dB)</label>
    <input id="limiter-input-level-input" inputmode="decimal" value="-3" />
  </div>
</div>

<div class="split-fields three">
  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="limiter-rms-input">RMS Time Constant (dB/s)</label>
    <input id="limiter-rms-input" inputmode="decimal" value="50" />
  </div>

  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="limiter-decay-input">Decay (dB/s)</label>
    <input id="limiter-decay-input" inputmode="decimal" value="12" />
  </div>

  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="limiter-output-gain">估算 Limiter Ratio / Gain</label>
    <input id="limiter-output-gain" readonly value="1" />
  </div>
</div>

<div class="status-line" data-status data-state="ok">
  <span aria-hidden="true">●</span>
  <span>等待处理</span>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel result-panel">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>结果抄写表</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="result-grid">
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>threshold</span>
      <strong data-limiter-result="threshold">-</strong>
      <em>Threshold 转线性值</em>
    </div>
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>RMS</span>
      <strong data-limiter-result="rms">-</strong>
      <em>RMS Time Constant 系数</em>
    </div>
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>decay</span>
      <strong data-limiter-result="decay">-</strong>
      <em>Decay 参数</em>
    </div>
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>decay complement</span>
      <strong data-limiter-result="decay-complement">-</strong>
      <em>1 - decay</em>
    </div>
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>limiter ratio</span>
      <strong data-limiter-result="ratio">-</strong>
      <em>按输入 RMS 估算的限制增益</em>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel">
  <label class="field-label" for="limiter-output">输出</label>
  <textarea id="limiter-output" readonly spellcheck="false" placeholder="计算结果会显示在这里"></textarea>
</div>
